          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] max-w-md leading-relaxed">
          Cada diseño que entregamos viene con su sistema. Los tokens de color, de tipografía y de espaciado pasan de Figma a Gutenberg sin la menor deformación.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 lg:gap-6">
        <!-- PANEL DE COLOR -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] p-7 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">/ Color</h3>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/60">5 / tokens</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {colours.map((c) => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] flex-shrink-0" style={`background:${c.hex}`}></div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-text-dark)] truncate">{c.name}</span>
                    <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)] flex-shrink-0">{c.hex}</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">{c.meaning}</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- PANEL DE TIPOGRAFÍA -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] p-7 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">/ Tipografía</h3>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/60">PingFang · Inter</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-5">
            {typeScale.map((t) => (
              <li class="flex items-baseline gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-[var(--color-surface-border)] last:border-0 last:pb-0">
                <div class="w-14 flex-shrink-0">
                  <div class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">{t.label}</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/60">{t.size}px</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-baseline gap-3">
                  <span class={`font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-none ${t.label === 'H1' ? 'text-2xl' : t.label === 'H2' ? 'text-lg' : t.label === 'Body' ? 'text-base' : 'text-xs'}`}>{t.cn}</span>
                  <span class={`text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-none ${t.label === 'H1' ? 'text-2xl' : t.label === 'H2' ? 'text-lg' : t.label === 'Body' ? 'text-base' : 'text-xs'}`}>{t.en}</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- PANEL DE ESPACIADO -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] p-7 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">/ Espaciado</h3>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/60">Escala base 4</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {spacingTokens.map((s) => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">{s.name}</div>
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
                  <div class={`h-2.5 bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/80 rounded-sm ${s.width}`}></div>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-7 pt-5 border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)] text-[11px] font-mono text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/70 leading-relaxed">
            Todo el espaciado parte de 4 px.<br/>Ritmo vertical fijado en 8 px.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

